    title: 'Slip Disc vs. Muscle Spasm — How Doctors Tell the Difference',
    excerpt: 'Learn the key symptoms and diagnostic methods used by specialists to differentiate between a slipped disc and a simple muscle spasm.',
    category: 'Orthopaedics',
    author: 'Dr. Gaurav Bhargava',
